# `changes/` is empty while no change is open.

A new SDD change drops its artifacts into a fresh directory here, e.g.
`openspec/changes/<change-id>/`. When the change is verified and approved,
`sdd-archive` moves the directory (with all its files) into
`openspec/changes/archive/<change-id>/` — see the `archive/README.md` index.

History so far (newest first):
- (none in flight)
- Archived: see `archive/`